 operator the phone number(s) (home, office, or cell) you want alerts on and specify the types of notifications (e.g., emergency alerts, traffic, health). The operator will add the number(s) to your Notify\u202fNYC account.\n3. **Update:** Call the same number to change notification types, phone numbers, email, address, or language.\n4. **Opt‑out:** Call 311 or\u202f212‑NEW‑YORK, provide the exact phone number used for registration, and request removal or full unsubscribe.\n\nYour phone number remains confidential and is used only for sending Notify\u202fNYC messages. This method works city‑wide across all five boroughs.', 'success': True, 'files_to_display': []}, 'interacted_element': None}])
